Uses of Package
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer

Packages that use com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client Defines the Rhizosphere visualization widget and all the main interfaces required to configure and instantiate a Rhizosphere visualization within GWT. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bootstrap Internal support classes to prepare and deploy Rhizosphere visualizations. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer Classes and interfaces for the generation and management of Rhizosphere renderings, that is, visual representation of Rhizosphere models. 
 

Classes in com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer used by com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client
NativeRenderer
          Bridge renderer that translates rendering instructions from RhizosphereRenderer instances into a native JSNI renderer that the Rhizosphere javascript library can understand.
RenderingOutput
          Helper interface that RhizosphereRenderer instances use to emit and customize the renderings they produce.
